<PageTitle>About | MarketGrowth</PageTitle>

<div class="mg-page">
    <h1>About MarketGrowth</h1>
    <p class="mg-subtitle">
        Smart market insights. Built for modern traders.
    </p>

    <section class="mg-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            MarketGrowth was created to make financial markets more accessible,
            transparent, and data driven. Our mission is to give traders and investors
            powerful tools to make better decisions.
        </p>
